able to say Black Lives

00:09:39.335 --> 00:09:41.460
Matter on the stage, and
being able to teach people

00:09:41.460 --> 00:09:44.910
that we have enough of a big
heart and enough of intellect

00:09:44.910 --> 00:09:47.460
for me to be able to say
