00:09:52.530 --> 00:09:53.680
we could do that.

00:09:53.680 --> 00:09:56.270
And that's for me what
intersectionality is at play,

00:09:56.270 --> 00:09:58.410
that we welcome people
with all their complexities

00:09:58.410 --> 00:09:58.800
to the table.

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:00.758
