leave any part of them

00:10:00.758 --> 00:10:03.540
out because it's not convenient
for the work or the movement

00:10:03.540 --> 00:10:05.759
or for quote 'social
justice' that everyone comes

00:10:05.759 --> 00:10:07.050
to the table within everything.

00:10:07.050 --> 00:10:10.560
If you don't accept all of me as
an intersectional human being,

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:12.660
then that's not the space
that I want to be in.

00:10:12.660 --> 00:10:12.960
